Hey, I'm going straight home.

211
00:14:04,843 --> 00:14:07,346
-I'm not in the mood to go to the office.
-Why not?

212
00:14:07,429 --> 00:14:08,847
Why aren't you in the mood?

213
00:14:08,931 --> 00:14:10,808
What is it? Tell me. What …

214
00:14:10,891 --> 00:14:12,184
Wait. Did you lose?

215
00:14:12,268 --> 00:14:13,394
Of course not.

216
00:14:13,936 --> 00:14:15,229
Right?

217
00:14:15,312 --> 00:14:16,355
You won, right?

218
00:14:16,438 --> 00:14:17,940
Yes, I knew it.

219
00:14:18,023 --> 00:14:20,109
You're tiring me out, man. I'm hanging up.

220
00:14:24,113 --> 00:14:24,947
Did they win?

221
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:27,074
What is this uneasy feeling?

222
00:14:57,187 --> 00:14:58,439
I'm home.

223
00:14:59,189 --> 00:15:00,774
Did your class run late?

224
00:15:01,358 --> 00:15:03,527
No, I went to an internet cafe
with a friend.

225
00:15:04,528 --> 00:15:05,529
Did you have fun?

226
00:15:05,613 --> 00:15:06,697
I'm sleepy.

227
00:15:07,907 --> 00:15:08,949
Hyeon-u.

228
00:15:09,617 --> 00:15:12,578
I made some sweet and sour pork
with a recipe I found online.

229
00:15:14,163 --> 00:15:15,497
It might be good.

230
00:15:21,170 --> 00:15:22,463
I'll go wash my hands.

231
00:15:24,048 --> 00:15:25,090
Okay.

232
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:41,607
How is it?

233
00:15:43,067 --> 00:15:44,276
It's good.

234
00:15:45,694 --> 00:15:47,196
Not bad for a first try, right?

235
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,323
Yes.

236
00:15:59,917 --> 00:16:01,210
Who am I going to live with?

237
00:16:05,297 --> 00:16:06,298
Me.

238
00:16:15,474 --> 00:16:17,101
Where's Dad?

239
00:16:20,104 --> 00:16:23,148
He's staying at a hotel near his office.

240
00:16:33,033 --> 00:16:33,909
I'm full.

241
00:16:35,869 --> 00:16:37,413
Okay, you don't have to finish it.

242
00:16:39,415 --> 00:16:40,708
Mom, are you sick?

243
00:16:41,667 --> 00:16:43,836
No, I'm not sick.

244
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,504
You don't look so well.

245
00:16:46,171 --> 00:16:47,840
No, I'm fine.

246
00:17:25,669 --> 00:17:26,670
I'm sorry.

247
00:17:39,391 --> 00:17:41,435
I'm so sorry.

248
00:17:42,978 --> 00:17:44,563
It was wrong of me.

249
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:22,434
She was in pain.

250
00:18:23,018 --> 00:18:24,353
I'm in pain too.

251
00:18:25,604 --> 00:18:27,189
I'll beg for his forgiveness

252
00:18:28,232 --> 00:18:29,525
until the day I die.

253
00:18:31,944 --> 00:18:33,320
I want to see Hyeon-u.

254
00:19:55,485 --> 00:19:56,653
That's bitter.

